Housekeeping Job – Dubai – Private Holiday House
My client is one of the most prestigious Families in Dubai. Currently, there is an opening for Housekeeping staff to join ASAP.
You will have previous experience from similar establishment / or experience from 5* properties on min. supervisory level.
Working hours: 8 hours per day and weekends off, unless the family is visiting – otherwise days off as per UAE Labour Law.
Salary package:
USD 2000 tax free
accommodation
transport
medical
annual flight home
Start ASAP.
To apply for Housekeeping Job – Dubai – Private Holiday House, send CV with recent photo and contactable references from similar employment.
ONLY SHORTLISTED CANDIDATES WILL BE CONTACTED.
